"
How
did
your
sketching
prosper,
Miss
Lewisham
?"

asked
Walter,
as
he
took
his
seat.

"
Not
very
well.
I
cannot
sketch
quickly.
A
crowd

of
children
just
let
out
of
school
came
round
us.
In

respect
of
crowding
and
staring,
German
children
are

no
better
than
English
ones."

not

things

delusion

better

?"
